citation.case_name: Emil Hansen, Permanent Receiver of Syracuse Sand Company, Inc. v. E. I. Du Pont De Nemours & Company, Inc. 1

html:
281 U.S. 751

50 S.Ct. 354

74 L.Ed. 1162

Emil HANSEN, Permanent Receiver of Syracuse Sand Company, Inc., petitioner,
v.
E. I. DU PONT DE NEMOURS & COMPANY, Inc.1

No. 758.

Supreme Court of the United States

May 5, 1930

1

Mr. Emil Hansen, pro se.

2

Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Circuit Court of Appeals for the Second Circuit denied.

1

The order sought to be reviewed here was a denial of motion to retax costs and no opinion thereon was filed in the court below. See, also, 33 F.(2d) 74 and 280 U. S. 589, 50 S. Ct. 37, 74 L. Ed. —.
